 2023-03052023-03-31NRCAN
ActCanadian Energy Regulator Act
PrecisReappointment of KATHY C. PENNEY of Calgary, Alberta, as a full-time Commissioner of the Canadian Energy Regulator, to hold office during good behaviour for a term of three years; and her designation as Deputy Lead Commissioner of the Canadian Energy Regulator, effective August 28, 2023.
